      <title>摩根士丹利的邓恩（Dunn）在哪里找到股票价值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-10/where-morgan-stanley-s-dunn-is-finding-value-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利投资管理公司（Morgan Stanley Investment Management）的价值权益联合和投资组合经理亚伦·邓恩（Aaron Dunn）讨论了他在当前市场环境中在“彭博社结束”上找到价值的地方。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-10/where-morgan-stanley-s-dunn-is-finding-value-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 20:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
